title: Camp WeWow - Water Week Day 5: Do The Leap Frog!
description:
It's Day 5 of Water Week, and we're hearing from campers who called in! To print your Make A Splash Water badge, head to tinkercast.com/camp. Then, come back next Monday for brand new episodes of Camp WeWow or catch up with this week's episodes on our new "WeWow" podcast feed.
